  "texts": [
    "For tasks requiring visual processing, the gpt-4-vision-preview (GPT-4V) model was used through the chat completions endpoint.",
    "The temperature value for both models was empirically set to 0.2 for the agent phase and 0.1 during RAG upon initial experimentation and no further modifications of model hyperparameters were performed.",
    "Additionally, for generating text embeddings, we used the latest version of OpenAI's embedding models, specifically the text-embedding-3-large model, which produces embeddings with a dimensionality of 3,072.",
    "To establish a baseline for comparison without tools and retrieval, we also evaluated GPT-4 with identical hyperparameters using a chain-of-thought reasoning module.",
    "Additionally, for model benchmarking, we used the Meta Llama-3 70B model (llama3-70b-8192) and Mistral's Mixtral 8x7B model (mixtral-8x7b-32768) through the Groq API, setting temperature values to 0.2 and the maximum number of output tokens to 4096."
  ],
